@startuml
[*] --> Registration: new users complete registration
Registration --> Registered: registration successful
Registered --> SignIn: registered users sign in
SignIn --> AccessGranted: access granted after signing in
AccessGranted --> Facilities: provide access to available facilities
AccessGranted --> NewsAndExpertContent: allow users to read news and expert content
AccessGranted --> HealthInfo: provide health-related information
HealthInfo --> ContinueOrFinish: allow users to continue using the system or finish the session
ContinueOrFinish --> FinishSession: user finishes the session
Registration --> AccessDenied: end access if registration fails
SignIn --> AccessDenied: end access if sign in fails
AccessGranted --> FinanceServices: process and validate insurance for available finance-related services
FinanceServices --> PaymentCheck: check payment with insurance for doctor consultations
PaymentCheck --> CompletePayment: complete the payment process
AccessGranted --> DrugAndSupplementPurchases: allow users to select payment methods (cash or insurance)
DrugAndSupplementPurchases --> CashPaymentDetails: inform users about cash payment details if chosen as the payment method
CompletePayment --> CollectFeedback: collect user feedback after service completion
FinishSession --> LogOut: log out users at the end of their session
@enduml
